						<p>The pictures of moon, sun, disc and counch are depicted. It records the construction of the temple for the god Hanumantadēva (Āñjanēya) and a <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> in front of the <hi rend="italic">garbha-guḍi.</hi></p>						

